      <title>美联储库克强调需要“谨慎”降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/fed-s-cook-emphasizes-need-for-cautious-approach-to-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事丽莎·库克表示，美联储必须采取谨慎的降息方式，以便为某些经济领域的通胀放缓留出更多时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/fed-s-cook-emphasizes-need-for-cautious-approach-to-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 14:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
